column8: The board software is not operating properly: The board software process is not successfully started. The product process is not operating properly: The product process cannot be scheduled in time or is not operating properly, causing  heartbeat messages not to be properly reported to the management process.  The subunit software is not operating properly: The link between the board subunit and main control unit is broken or the subunit software is not operating properly, causing heartbeat messages not to be properly reported to the main control unit.
